      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 76.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 76.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>柔弱處上。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Therefore the place of what is firm and strong is below, and that of what is soft and weak is above.</seg>
      </tuv>
